â”‚   â”‚-- routes/
â”‚   â”‚-- controllers/
â”‚-- README.md  # Project Documentation
```

---
## **How It Works? âš™ï¸**
1. **Paste your long URL** in the input box.
2. Click the **"Shorten URL"** button to generate a short link.
3. Optionally, generate a **QR code** for the link.
4. Use the **SMS feature** to share the short URL via Twilio API.

---
## **Installation & Setup** ğŸ’»
Follow these steps to run the project on your local machine:

### **1ï¸âƒ£ Clone the Repository**
```sh
git clone https://github.com/your-username/narrow-links.git
cd narrow-links
```

### **2ï¸âƒ£ Install Dependencies**
#### **For Frontend**
```sh
cd client
npm install
```
#### **For Backend**
```sh
cd server
npm install
```

### **3ï¸âƒ£ Start the Application**
#### **Run Backend**
```sh
cd server
npm start
```
#### **Run Frontend**
```sh
cd client
npm start
```

The project will now be running at **http://localhost:3000/** ğŸ‰

